_json.gridTitle: The Water And Light Lawn Show - Hammacher Schlemmer
_json.description: The Water And Light Lawn Show.  This is the mister that casts a color-changing spray, transforming a lawn into an effervescent water and light show. As water flows through the mister it propels a turbine generator that powers the color changing LEDs and pressurizes the water, producing a 6 1/2' high by 19 1/3' wide plume of fine mist that seamlessly transitions from red to blue to green to yellow to purple.A wonderful way to water your lawn.
